E414.description: We have taken their important territory. It's unluckily they will agree to peace anytime soon.

E357.title: Texas declared independence
E357.description: They used our weakness in this moment.

E263.title: Fall of the Soviet Union
E263.description: USSR crashed. Apparently, there is no such country who can win against the Reich.

E962.title: Mexico is capitulated
E962.description: We took Mexico. They can't fight anymore.

E355.title: Gap in America
E355.answer1: Give the changes to this place!
E355.answer2: I won't betray the real America!
E355.description: Due to the abrupt change of government the civil war has been started in AC.

E270.title: Transportation issues
E270.description: This winter turned out to be really cold. Issues with the long-road transportation are followed from this.

E282.title: Drowning in protests
E282.description: Students and young people are protesting en masse because of our "agressive" politic. They don't want war. Most of them are republic-party supporters.
E282.answer3: They'll shout and then calm down.

E262.title: Route of Reich
E262.description: Most of their big cities are crushed or captured. Their resistance is useless. There was no stopping us.

E983.title: We are being accused
E983.description: Soviet Union accused our government of corruption.

E331.title: The Battle for Moscow
E331.description: The enemy is already at the capital. We need to spend a lot of money to save the capital. But if everything is under control, we can do without it.

E267.title: Victory of the traditionalists
E267.description: They has successfully won the chinesse civil war. China is united again.

E977.title: Bulgaria is capitulated
E977.description: We took Sofia. They can't fight anymore.

E375.title: Liberation of Austria
E375.description: We saved some nations from extinct after this war.

E271.title: Leningrad has fallen
E271.description: We have lost the control of the Leningrad.

E401.title: Liberation of Italy
E401.description: We saved some nations from extinct after this war.

E119.title: Netherlands denied our terms.
E119.description: Is this a provocation to war?

E917.title: Attempted assassination
E917.description: Group of Alabama's terrorists attempted assassination on offical in New-York.
E917.description1: The offical was killed and culprit was not found.
E917.description2: The offical was injured and the culprit was eliminated.

E179.title: Breaking though Czechoslovakia
E179.description: Germany attacked Czechoslovakia. The official reason was the proposal from the Soviet Union to conclude a military alliance.

E260.title: Italy has started a new war
E260.description: Italian-Yougoslavian war has started because of a mysterious border conflict.

E291.title: Belgium declared independence
E291.description: They used our weakness in this moment.

E388.title: Northern strike
E388.description: Sweden had announced the declaration about war against the Soviets.

E258.title: Canada accepted to hold a referendum
E258.description: And most people liked our idea.

E124.title: Baltic-Soviet War
E124.description: Quite recently Soviet Union attacked Lithuania, Latvia and Estonia because of their enemy rhetoric.

E117.title: We got ultimatum from Germany
E117.description: They want us to join them.

E123.title: Norway is capitulated
E123.description: We took Oslo. They can't fight anymore.

E167.title: Non-motivational military
E167.description: Our soldiers don't want to fight, they have no motivation. Many of them agree with the protesters.

E264.title: Fall of the German Reich
E264.description: Reich crashed. Apparently, there is no such country who can win against the Soviets.

E984.title: Turkey is capitulated
E984.description: We took Ankara. They can't fight anymore.

E011.title: Economic crisis
E011.description: The Great War severely damaged our economy, we supported our allies for a long time, thereby ruining our country. Because of this, nationolists interests also growing there.

E387.title: Operation: "White"
E387.description: It's time to start an invansion from the North.

E261.title: Route of Soviet Union
E261.description: Most of their big cities are crushed or captured. Their resistance is useless. There was no stopping us.

E079.title: Voroshilov is fully entrenched
E079.description: Thing are really getting better in the country!

E152.title: Referendum
E152.description: Moldovans clearly want to join us, so we can hold a referendum.

E122.title: Baltic issue
E122.description: Governments of Litva, Latvia and Estonia are hostile to us and hindering our trade relations on the Baltic Sea. There is a possibility that they can go under the German influence. We need to solve this issue as soon as we can.
E122.answer3: It's not in our best interest.

E200.title: "Vector" - military union
E200.description: Germany has announced a new worldwide alliance for changing the world order.

E253.title: The war with Soviet Union
E253.description: We have started the total war with Soviet Union. No mercy.

E307.title: Union Berlin-Moscow and Vector
E307.answer1: There are no enemies with such allies.
E307.description: Germany offers us extensive opportunities in their military alliance. We will almost rule half the world, according to them. But in return, we will have to deal with the UK. Do we agree?

E399.title: Liberation of Sweden and Norway
E399.description: We saved some nations from extinct after this war.

E121.title: Oligarchy
E121.answer1: Strengthen the power of the rich
E121.description: You can concentrate the power in the hands of the rich.

E319.title: Revenue from the Bosphorus Strait
E319.description: We get a lot of money by controlling this place.

E169.title: We are in power!
E169.description: We won this civil war, but the country will have to rehabilitated.

E321.title: The style of war
E321.description: This must be our most difficult and longest war. So we need to choose a style of war that we will follow.

E279.title: Log in to the game
E279.description: A lot of huge-importance countries already joint Vector military alliance, but we are still not one of them. Is that good condition?

E009.title: Operation "Pacific"
E009.description: Russian state contradict our laws and rules. We can't ingore it. It's time to take action.

E379.title: Heavy desertion
E379.description: Most of soldier thinks they are actually German and Austrian nation is not exist.

E003.title: Agreements with the Confederates
E003.answer2: So that we pay debts for them?
E003.description: In case something goes wrong, we need a strong ally like the confederates of America, don't we?

E006.title: Our army was abolished
E006.answer1: Only German army will protect us
E006.description: Our former officers were shooted and most of soldiers went to jail or were killed too.

E243.title: Corruption
E243.description: There is a problem with mass corruption in our country.

E403.title: Refugees from all over the world
E403.answer1: At least we're good at something.
E403.description: Due to the current political situation in the world, many people want to flee as far as possible from the fighting. And we're far from it.

E255.title: Annexation of Canada
E255.description: Independent Canada depends on us in many ways. They are weaker economical and in military terms. Its population would like to be annexed, I am pretty sure.

E194.title: German invansion of Poland
E194.description: In response to the Soviet invasion of Lithuania, Latvia, and Estonia, Germany decided to occupy Polish territories in order to prevent a conspiracy against the German people and protect Germany itself.

E328.title: Jubilation in the West
E328.description: Feasts are currently taking place in the Russian Kingdom, in honor of our failures. They believe that our defeat will lead socialism out of Russia.

civilization_242.name: Movement for the Emancipation of the Niger Delta
